  "rationale": "<p>From 5p/q = 8.4, we get p/q = 1.68. From p/(qm) = 33.6, we get (p/q)(1/m) = 33.6, so 1.68/m = 33.6, giving m = 1.68/33.6 = 0.05 = 1/20.</p>",
